<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: megascarab -->
  <Megascarab.label>巨甲蟲</Megascarab.label>
  <!-- EN: A genetically-engineered war insect that resembles a massive beetle. Once the worker caste of an artificial ecosystem of insects designed to fight mechanoid invasions, it is less deadly than its larger cousins. Still, its size and hard shell make it dangerous when it attacks. A eusocial creature, it cannot reproduce individually.\n\nEngineered to thrive in mechanoid-ravaged environments, war insects like this move faster after being exposed to polluted terrain. -->
  <Megascarab.description>一種基因改造的甲蟲，原本被用以抵御機器人入侵，一般單獨行動。牠的尺寸和硬殼使牠們成為一種非常危險的生物。</Megascarab.description>
  <!-- EN: mandibles -->
  <Megascarab.tools.mandibles.label>下顎</Megascarab.tools.mandibles.label>
  <!-- EN: head -->
  <Megascarab.tools.head.label>頭</Megascarab.tools.head.label>
  
  <!-- EN: megaspider -->
  <Megaspider.label>巨蛛</Megaspider.label>
  <!-- EN: Not actually a spider, the megaspider is a genetically-engineered giant insect the size of a bear. Its thick chitinous armor makes it hard to kill, while its long ripper-blades make it deadly at close quarters. It is, however, quite slow in open terrain.\n\nEngineered to fight mechanoids in toxic environments, war insects like this move faster after being exposed to polluted terrain. -->
  <Megaspider.description>實際上並非蜘蛛，這熊一般大小的蟲族是基因工程製造出的產物，原本被設計用來進行粗重的工作及戰鬥。厚重的外殼使牠難以被殺死，一對長而鋒利的鐮刀爪使牠在戰鬥中非常致命。</Megaspider.description>
  <!-- EN: insect meat -->
  <Megaspider.race.meatLabel>蟲肉</Megaspider.race.meatLabel>
  <!-- EN: head claw -->
  <Megaspider.tools.head_claw.label>角</Megaspider.tools.head_claw.label>
  <!-- EN: head -->
  <Megaspider.tools.head.label>頭</Megaspider.tools.head.label>
  
  <!-- EN: spelopede -->
  <Spelopede.label>穴行蟲</Spelopede.label>
  <!-- EN: A medium-sized bioengineered insectoid the size of a sheep. The spelopede is the middle caste of a hive, taking care of most work tasks as well as fighting with its digging claws. It's dangerous in combat, but slow on open ground.\n\nEngineered to thrive in mechanoid-ravaged environments, war insects like this move faster after being exposed to polluted terrain. -->
  <Spelopede.description>這種生化工程製造出的蟲族有和羊等大的體型。穴行蟲在蟲穴中屬於中層階級，包辦大多數的工作並用牠挖掘用的爪子保衛蟲巢。</Spelopede.description>
  <!-- EN: head claw -->
  <Spelopede.tools.head_claw.label>角</Spelopede.tools.head_claw.label>
  <!-- EN: head -->
  <Spelopede.tools.head.label>頭</Spelopede.tools.head.label>
  
</LanguageData>